init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's all in fun, of course.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But when they changed the mug rankings, they didn't expect people to treat it so seriously.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: were amazed at the amount of people who called them to complain that they had been personally offended by the new mug rankings.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: There are even people who have bought the mug on purpose to taunt their wives and mothers-in-law.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The company still has very high hopes for the campaign.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: By the end of the year, there will be entire sets of "Best Mom", "Most Handsome Dad", and "Bossiest

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Once this campaign is done, people will be seeing the mug rankings everywhere.
